{"tid":1104190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女乘客突嬌嗔喊「不要」 小黃司機嚇壞一句話讓她閉嘴","createTime":"2019-04-13T03:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T07:09:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdfd7a630034712f5b744b4fa1153d7fb728522","tid":1104190,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFKNG_V5YZY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKFKNG_V5YZY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=87c0e235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFKNG_V5YZY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n一名女子搭乘計程車，下車前卻發出嬌喘聲音，還頻喊著「不要」，嚇壞司機。 <br />\n<br />\n社會新聞常會看到有計程車司機遭到乘客毆打或搶劫傷害，為了保護自己，多數的司機都<br />\n會在車上錄影自保。有網友在臉書「爆料公社」貼出一段影片，一名女子搭乘計程車到目的地後拿出信用卡付車資，但當司機刷完卡要把卡片交還給女乘客時，<br />\n<br />\n這名女子突然嬌嗔頻喊「不要！不要啦」，嚇得司機趕緊表明車上有錄影，女子聽了頓時安靜了下來，然後就默默地下車。許多網友看了影片覺得很傻眼，紛紛猜測這名女子的真正用意。<br />\n<br />\n影片一開始，這名戴著眼鏡和口罩的女乘客在計程車上還跟司機正常地聊天，到了目的地後，女子表示要刷卡並且拿出卡片給司機。司機刷完卡後要交還卡片時，這名女子突然低下頭，接著身體疑似在扭動，並發出嬌嗔呻吟的聲音，不斷地喊著「不要&hellip;不要啦」，司機嚇得問女子怎麼了？接著表明說車上有錄影，女子一聽到有錄影馬上安靜了下來，然後就默默地開門下車離開。<br />\n<br />\nPO影片的網友說<br />\n<br />\n「好險這位司機大哥有車內攝影機不然就慘了」，<br />\n<br />\n其他網友看了也大罵「幹嘛？鬼附身喔？」、「直接報警比較快」、「司機應該讓她多演一下，看她到底想幹嗎」、「要是司機沒說有攝影機，不知道劇情會如何發展？」<br />\n<br />\n還有人猜測這名女子的目的，「這是新的手法嗎？」、<br />\n<br />\n「想陷害司機大哥嗎？」、「騙成功吃一年」、「妹子扭腰喊不要，故事肯定不簡單」、<br />\n<br />\n「她戴著耳機，是不是在和誰聊天？而電話那頭的人用遠端操控情趣用品，所以那個人才在喊不要？」"},{"pid":"cfbc0699029da668968672260eee594fcb84c08e","tid":1104190,"uid":113830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚醜 嗌不要不要 好作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349965144afdeb6e1225e8549066496254c7902d","tid":1104190,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:27:31.000Z","msg":"台妹d叫床聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce78b1d234becb0a67ed599ff42ad5beee0dfb33","tid":1104190,"uid":232594,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"係咪裝左遙控震蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男朋友撳左去最大力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2fd54e65d5885c567e322b3c2da198acc815d5","tid":1104190,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce78b1d234becb0a67ed599ff42ad5beee0dfb33","tid":1104190,"uid":232594,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"係咪裝左遙控震蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男朋友撳左去最大力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"佢啲行為似有啲唔舒服，可能「異物」影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d98d86ed02d9ed91d5dc0df5e5fd136b16e7850","tid":1104190,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xkb8QG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xkb8QG.gif&h=02ccea24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e10c150ccc788fd6fadd50aa877a4ee2dc